@host = http://localhost:8081
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Get account (requires INSTITUTION role)
GET {{@host}}/api/account
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}

### Get admin info (requires ADMIN role)
GET {{@host}}/api/account/account/admin?param=foo
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}

### Check account (throws 403 if param missing)
GET {{@host}}/api/account/account/check?param=test
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}
